events.title: MTG Standard
events.description: Join us every Wednesday for 4-5 rounds of Magic the Gathering Pioneer!Entry is only $5, or $8 with a standard booster pack of your choice. Registration starts at 6:00pm with gameplay shortly after at 7:00pm! Sign up 60 minutes early and receive an extra stamp!
